woo This class represents a value used by the SQL tags. It contains default implementations of get methods for all supported types, to avoid casting when using a concrete implementation. All default implementations throw an UnsupportedConversionException. Each subclass must override the getString() method, returning the value as a String, plus the get method for the appropriate data type, and provide a constructor to set the value.
